ing%20tools.%20I%20tried%20one%20of%20them%20and%20we%20built%20our%20first%20clickable%20prototype.%20We%20could%20iterate%20on%20that%20with%20the%20client%20and%20automate%20the%20warehouse%20in%20a%20very%20MVP%20manner.%20That%20was%20my%20first%20dabble%20into%20product%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20that%20has%20applied%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consultant-translation-documents-ai-startup-bluente-daphne-tay-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20I%20build%20Bluente%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20think%20about%20product%20design%2C%20how%20to%20build%20a%20minimum%20viable%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consulting-tips-for-getting-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAt%20Bain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20dealt%20with%20many%20established%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20There's%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%20about%20building%20a%20solid%20marketing%20and%20sales%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec7ee659-8a2c-4653-bc57-8bae6ef5e0c3%5C%22%3EWhat%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20from%20scratch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20thing%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20was%20sales.%20At%20Bain%2C%20we%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20influencing%20people%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20create%20analytical%20work%20that%20could%20influence%20a%20client%20in%20a%20certain%20direction.%20But%20you're%20never%20actively%20selling%20until%20you%20get%20to%20partner%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20Bluente%2C%20one%20of%20my%20advisors%20told%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20go%20out%20and%20sell%20the%20company%2C%20no%20one%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20may%20buy%20and%20believe%20in%20you%2C%20but%20that%20alone%20doesn't%20create%20a%20repeatable%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20we've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangel-investor-startup-playbooks-silicon-valley-immad-akhund-2025-8%5C%22