46b-9bca-82a9d08b63d0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20PetSafe%20Easy%20Walk%20Comfort%20Harness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20followed%20the%20brand's%20size%20guide%20for%20Roo's%20measurements%20and%20ordered%20a%20medium%2C%20which%20fit%20her%20perfectly.%20The%20straps%20were%20easy%20to%20adjust%2C%20allowing%20the%20harness%20to%20lie%20snug%20against%20her%20frame%20without%20shifting%20from%20side%20to%20side.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20struggled%20to%20find%20the%20right%20fit%20for%20other%20harnesses%2C%20which%20have%20rubbed%20against%20Roo's%20elbows%20and%20caused%20some%20chaffing.%20After%20using%20the%20harness%20for%20several%20months%2C%20we%20haven't%20encountered%20this%20issue%20at%20all%2C%20even%20when%20the%20harness%20gets%20wet%20during%20river%20romps.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20left%2C%20a%20tan%20dog%20wearing%20a%20green%20harness%20is%20looking%20up%20with%20ears%20perked%20while%20on%20leash%20next%20to%20a%20person's%20shoes%2C%20and%20on%20the%20right%2C%20the%20dog%20is%20standing%20in%20grass%20wearing%20the%20harness%20and%20a%20patterned%20bandana%20and%20facing%20forward.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c89130f9db348adc0b8465%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoo%20walks%20on%20a%20loosh%20leash%20beside%20me%20while%20wearing%20the%20PetSafe%20Easy%20Walk%20Comfort%20harness%20(left).%20The%20harness%20is%20designed%20to%20reduce%20pulling%20when%20the%20leash%20is%20attached%20to%20the%20front%20D-ring%20(right).%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Holbrook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20soft%2C%20flexible%20padding%20also%20fits%20comfortably%20against%20her%20body%2C%20unlike%20the%20stiffer%20cardboard-like%20padding%20of%20other%20harnesses%